date 11 July 2001
new app-admin/metalog-0.6
A syslogd/klogd replacement.  Very full featured, including logging
based on facility, program name and regex.
jerry

date 9 July 2001
new net-misc/pdnsd-1.1.6
Proxy DNS server with permanent caching (saves state/cache between stop
and start).
jerry

date 6 July 2001
upd sys-apps/iproute2-2.2.4-r2 to 2.2.4-r3
Remove reference to ETH_P_ECHO, which is no longer in the kernel.
Programs now compile and work.
jerry

date 5 July 2001
new x11-terms/root-tail-0.0.10
Terminal program that displays multiple log files with multiple colors
on an X sessions root window.
jerry

date 4 July 2001
upd net-ftp/pure-ftpd-0.98.7-r2
Modified to make pure-ftpd start properly with xinetd

upd net-misc/bind-9.1.2-r1
Modified to have the default installed named up and running. added root.cache/localhost & 127.0.0 files as well modified default named.conf with more parametersin it & modified named to start with user named.

